                <h1>Pharmaceutical company Roivant Sciences collaborates with Duke community in drug research </h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/9469c76b-0c20-4481-9967-b5ebfe90ced6.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="Roivant,&#x20;Durham,&#x20;NC" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            Roivant, Durham, NC

                                                             <aside class="photo-caption photo-credit d-block pl-1">
                                    <figcaption class="d-block">
